'''Surface Pro 3'''是[[Microsoft_Surface|Surface Pro]]系列第三代产品，由[[微软|微软]]設計開發並推出販售的平板電腦，于2014年6月10日发布。<ref name="Verge">{{cite web |first=Tom |last=Warren |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/20/5734102/surface-pro-3-features-pricing-announcement |title=Microsoft announces the Surface Pro 3 |publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=May 20, 2014 |accessdate=May 20, 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208204045/http://www.theverge.com/2014/5/20/5734102/surface-pro-3-features-pricing-announcement |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Microsoft">{{cite press release |title=Microsoft introduces Surface Pro 3: the tablet that can replace your laptop |url=http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/news/press/2014/may14/05-20surfacepr.aspx |date=May 20, 2014 |location=New York |publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]] |accessdate=May 21, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521041841/http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/news/press/2014/may14/05-20surfacepr.aspx |archive-date=2014-05-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CBCTS">{{cite news |title=Surface Pro 3: Microsoft's new tablet aims at laptop market |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/surface-pro-3-microsoft-s-new-tablet-aims-at-laptop-market-1.2648243 |work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |date=May 20, 2014 |accessdate=May 20, 2014 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402010106/http://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/surface-pro-3-microsoft-s-new-tablet-aims-at-laptop-market-1.2648243 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最初Surface Pro 3運行的作業系統是[[Windows_8_Pro|Windows 8 Pro]]，2015年後升級至[[Windows_10_Pro|Windows 10 Pro]]。<ref name=Win10AlreadyOn>{{cite news|last1=Callaham|first1=John|title=Windows 10 is now pre-installed when you buy Surface 3 and Surface Pro 3 tablets|url=http://www.windowscentral.com/windows-10-now-pre-installed-when-you-buy-surface-3-and-surface-pro-3-tablets|accessdate=3 December 2015|work=Windows Central|publisher=Mobile Nations|date=4 August 2015|archive-date=2017-10-21|archive